	(text "C_{0} = 0.68~1.02pF\nC_{L} = 10pF\nESR = 4 Ohm\ng_{m} = 7.5mA/V (Gain margin) requit par le MCU.\ng_{mcrit} = 4*ESR*(2πF)²*(C_{0}+C_{L})² = 1.23 mA/V\ng_{mcrit} correspond a la transductance\nminimal pour que les oscilations perdures.\ngain_{margin} = g_{m} / g_{mcrit} = 7.5/1.23 = 6.11\nST recommande gain_{margin} > 5 \nce qui est le cas pour ce cristal."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 13.97 110.49 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 0.9525 0.9525)
				(italic yes)
			)
			(justify left top)
		)
		(uuid "47398941-0cc5-460d-9298-83548c150c8e")
	)
